author: slive
msg: Adjust the mirror selection CGI so that it uses the last update
time of the mirror database as the basis for determining if a
mirror is sufficiently fresh.  With this change, if the mirror
database stops getting updated, all the fresh mirrors will remain
fresh and all the old ones will remain old.

author: ekoneil
msg: Package protect the implementation classes for the default data grid configuration.
These are now creatable only by the DefaultDataGridConfig class.
